    "body" : "<p>Use <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/io/File.html#createTempFile%28java.lang.String,%20java.lang.String%29\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>File.createTempFile()</code></a>.</p>\n\n<pre><code>File tempFile = File.createTempFile(\"prefix-\", \"-suffix\");\n//File tempFile = File.createTempFile(\"MyAppName-\", \".tmp\");\ntempFile.deleteOnExit();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Will create a file in the temp dir, like:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>prefix-6340763779352094442-suffix</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
